Football,API,provides,a,live,scoring,service,for,a,variety,of,football,leagues,including,the,english,premier,league,European,leagues,major,world,leagues,and,competitions,including,the,world,cup,The,Football,API,allows,users,to,make,REST,calls,to,get,current,tournament,standings,get,scheduled,match,lists,and,get,live,scoring,An,account,is,required,with,service